'''Kureh''' ({{lang-fa|<U+0643><U+0648><U+0631><U+0647>}}, also [[Romanize]]d as '''K<U+016B>reh''')<ref>{{GEOnet3|-3792707|Kureh}}</ref> is a village in [[Layl Rural District]], in the [[Central District (Lahijan County)|Central District]] of [[Lahijan County]], [[Gilan Province]], [[Iran]]. At the 2006 census, its population was 154, in 48 families.<ref>{{IranCensus2006|01}}</ref>  

